oman in casual attire walking by a large weaving loom with black threads in a bright, clean room" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 960px) 45vw, (max-width: 1440px) 30vw, 430px" srcSet="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/cbef8ad9-7d20-4974-a8e5-104cc8f33833/essay-v1-_dsc8254.jpg?width=256&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 256w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/cbef8ad9-7d20-4974-a8e5-104cc8f33833/essay-v1-_dsc8254.jpg?width=384&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 384w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/cbef8ad9-7d20-4974-a8e5-104cc8f33833/essay-v1-_dsc8254.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 640w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/cbef8ad9-7d20-4974-a8e5-104cc8f33833/essay-v1-_dsc8254.jpg?width=750&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 750w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/cbef8ad9-7d20-4974-a8e5-104cc8f33833/essay-v1-_dsc8254.jpg?width=828&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 828w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/cbef8ad9-7d20-4974-a8e5-104cc8f33833/essay-v1-_dsc8254.jpg?width=1080&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1080w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/cbef8ad9-7d20-4974-a8e5-104cc8f33833/essay-v1-_dsc8254.jpg?width=1200&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1200w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/cbef8ad9-7d20-4974-a8e5-104cc8f33833/essay-v1-_dsc8254.jpg?width=1920&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1920w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/cbef8ad9-7d20-4974-a8e5-104cc8f33833/essay-v1-_dsc8254.jpg?width=2048&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 2048w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/cbef8ad9-7d20-4974-a8e5-104cc8f33833/essay-v1-_dsc8254.jpg?width=3840&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 3840w" src="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/cbef8ad9-7d20-4974-a8e5-104cc8f33833/essay-v1-_dsc8254.jpg?width=3840&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto"/></div><div class="sc-27019820-1 igZijh"><div class="sc-27019820-6 ioJvx"><div class="group z-[